ate employees on their rights and responsibilities as well as the consequences of conflict on their own lives.', 'Urgent need for conflict resolution on Lonmin mines', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '811-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-25 17:50:53', '2013-10-25 15:50:53', '', 811, 'http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/news/uncategorized/811-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
