(1065, 2, '2013-11-27 10:01:29', '2013-11-27 08:01:29', '<p style="text-align: center;">Over the years OIM has developed a unique, integrated approach to business performance management\r\nand strategy execution in these core areas. With a solid track record of working with blue-chip companies both locally and abroad,\r\nour multidisciplinary team eliminates the need to call in various business consultants.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Furthermore, our proven methodologies and way of working ensure that we can play an integral part\r\nin the continuous evolvement, progress and success of your business.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 10:01:29', '2013-11-27 08:01:29', '', 258, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1066, 2, '2013-11-27 10:03:15', '2013-11-27 08:03:15', '<div>\r\n\r\nBusiness performance specialists Operational Improvement Management (OIM) advises several South African blue-chip companies and has managed assignments in Europe, Australia, America and other African countries.\r\n\r\nWith a proven track record dating back to 1985, we specialise in the key areas of people management, organisational improvement and operations management.\r\n\r\nOver the years OIM has developed a unique, integrated approach to business performance management and strategy execution in these areas. We believe our model focuses on the main elements of a successful organisation and provides a framework for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategy definition</li>\r\n	<li>Business architecture and alignment</li>\r\n	<li>Effective leadership and talent management</li>\r\n	<li>Employee relations and stakeholder engagement</li>\r\n	<li>Operations management, optimisation and continuous improvement</li>\r\n	<li>Performance measurement and improvement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur multidisciplinary team offers seamless implementation of these elements, obviating the need for calling in various business consultants with incompatible methodologies and confusing terminologies.\r\n\r\nBut don’t take our word for it – <a title="Contact" href="../clients/">read what our clients have to say</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'About OIM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '279-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 10:03:15', '2013-11-27 08:03:15', '', 279, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/279-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1067, 2, '2013-11-27 10:04:10', '2013-11-27 08:04:10', 'OIM has a proven track record in many countries, across several continents and industries.\r\n\r\nWe have built long-term partnerships with many of our clients who trust us implicitly to help create sustainable solutions and, as a result, have referred business associates to us.\r\n\r\nWe also take pride in how several of our clients have consistently excelled in the prestigious Deloitte Best Company to Work For Survey. PPC Cement, for example, was the winner in the category best manufacturing company for five years running and was named top South African employer in 2005. Both Robor (2011, 2010 &amp; 2009) and Plascon (2008) scooped the best manufacturing award, while Barloworld Logistics twice came out tops in the category best logistics, shipping and transport.\r\n<h2>Industries and Countries</h2>\r\nWe have completed assignments in countries such as Australia, Belgium, Botswana, France, Germany, the Netherlands, Spain, the UK, America, Namibia, Malawi, Mauritius, Nigeria and Zimbabwe.\r\n\r\nThese assignments covered a wide spectrum of industries, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Education</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering</li>\r\n	<li>Food</li>\r\n	<li>IT and telecommunication</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial</li>\r\n	<li>Manufacturing</li>\r\n	<li>Mining</li>\r\n	<li>Public sector (regional government)</li>\r\n	<li>Retail</li>\r\n	<li>Financial services</li>\r\n	<li>Tobacco, wine &amp; spirits</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Clients', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 10:04:10', '2013-11-27 08:04:10', '', 286, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/286-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1068, 2, '2013-11-27 10:06:14', '2013-11-27 08:06:14', '<div>\r\n\r\nOIM prides itself in its ability to deliver results and has a strong commitment to service delivery. As such, we place a high premium on the quality of our consultants and team members.\r\n\r\nWe offer career opportunities for people with proven experience and relevant academic qualifications in the areas of:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Organisational performance improvement</li>\r\n	<li>Human resources / employee relations / organisational development / learning &amp; development</li>\r\n	<li>Operations management</li>\r\n	<li>Leadership development and talent management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you fit this bill and have a willingness to travel quite extensively you are welcome to contact us! Also keep an eye on our <a href="http://za.linkedin.com/company/oim-international-pty-ltd?trk=ppro_cprof" target="_blank">LinkedIN page</a> where we post most of our vacancies.\r\n\r\nFor more information, or to submit your CV, please mail Suzanne van Zyl at <a href="mailto:svanzyl@oimgroup.com">svanzyl@oimgroup.com</a> or call her on +27 21 913 8814/5.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Careers at OIM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '299-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 10:06:14', '2013-11-27 08:06:14', '', 299, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/299-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1069, 2, '2013-11-27 10:07:17', '2013-11-27 08:07:17', '<img src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/umbono.gif" alt="umbono" width="164" height="44" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-783" />\r\n\r\nOIM Umbono Mining Solutions is a joint venture between OIM and Umbono Capital, combining the unique skills and experience of the two companies to unlock operational efficiency in the mining industry.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.oimumbono.com/" target="_blank">www.oimumbono.com</a> and <a href="http://www.umbono.com/" target="_blank">www.umbono.com</a> for more information.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-325" alt="Pure Survey" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/pure.gif" width="222" height="37" />\r\n\r\nAs one of South Africa’s leaders on online surveys for customers, employees and market research, we have partnered with Pure Survey to provide affordable, innovative and effective stakeholder perception surveys. Surveys are customised for each client’s unique needs and the main goal is useful reporting and data analysis that you, as the customer, require to effectively measure and manage your environment.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.puresurvey.co.za/" target="_blank">www.puresurvey.co.za</a> for more information.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\nIn offering our leadership assessment and development interventions we have teamed up with several leading international talent management houses.\r\n<div style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-326" alt="Saville Consulting" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/saville.gif" width="265" height="36" />\r\n\r\nSaville Consulting develops rigorous and work-relevant assessment tools that measure the critical fit between individuals, job requirements and workplace culture.\r\n\r\nFor more information on this leader in its field, visit <a href="http://www.savilleconsulting.co.za" target="_blank">www.savilleconsulting.co.za.</a>\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-327" alt="Shl" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shl.gif" width="76" height="47" />\r\n\r\nShl, a global leader in talent measurement, offers employment testing tools and employee development assessment services.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.shl.com/" target="_blank">www.shl.com</a> for information on their extensive solutions and expertise.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-328" alt="Insights" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/insights.gif" width="63" height="75" />\r\n\r\nEveryone who has ever worked in a team-driven environment understands the importance of solid relations and work methods to get things done.\r\n\r\nWith Insight’s international track record spanning 20 years, we use the Insights® methodology to improve team effectiveness at our clients. It helps people to learn about themselves and others in a practical, results-driven way using colours and fun exercises.\r\n\r\nRead more about this methodology and case studies at <a href="http://www.insights.com" target="_blank">www.insights.com.</a>', 'Partnerships', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '320-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 10:07:17', '2013-11-27 08:07:17', '', 320, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/320-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
