(1098, 2, '2013-12-05 14:33:50', '2013-12-05 12:33:50', '<p style="text-align: center;">Over the years OIM has developed a unique, integrated approach to business performance management\r\nand strategy execution in these core areas. With a solid track record of working with blue-chip companies both locally and abroad,\r\nour multidisciplinary team eliminates the need to call in various business consultants.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Furthermore, our proven methodologies and way of working ensure that we can play an integral part\r\nin the continuous evolvement, progress and success of your business.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 14:33:50', '2013-12-05 12:33:50', '', 258, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/OIM_2014/news/uncategorized/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
